<fieldset
  *ngFor="let one_sheep of sheep"
  routerLink="/sheep/{{ one_sheep.name.toLowerCase() }}"
>
  <legend>{{ one_sheep.name }}</legend>
  <dl>
    <dt>Title</dt>
    <dl>{{ one_sheep.title }}</dl>
    <dt>Tagline</dt>
    <dl>{{ one_sheep.tagline }}</dl>
  </dl>
</fieldset>
import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core';
import { Observable } from 'rxjs';
import { SheepServiceService } from '../services/sheep-service.service';
import { Sheep } from '../types';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-sheep',
  templateUrl: './sheep.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./sheep.component.scss'],
})
export class SheepComponent implements OnInit {
  sheep: Sheep[];

  constructor(private sheepServiceService: SheepServiceService) {

    this.sheepServiceService.load().subscribe();

    this.sheep = [{ title: 'I am a sheep', name: 'Wooly', tagline: 'Baaaaa' }];
  }
}
